  "texts": [
    "For all other classification tasks, we only train on the specific subset.",
    "For example, if we want to classify BCC vs. SCC vs.",
    "AK vs. SK, we train a classifier only on the BCC, SCC, AK, and SK training features and ignore the remaining classes.",
    "Some datasets (Queensland and Linköping) only provide annotation masks as labels.",
    "They may contain different disease labels for different regions in the same slide."
